{
  "id": "adv_event_2308_01_03",
  "title": "おしごとシークレット 3話 パパと呼ばれし者",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ありえないよ。優に限って、パパ活なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. There's no chance Yu would do something like a sugar daddy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "私だって、信じたくないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to believe it either‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8120184262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "優は思慮深い女の子だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu is a thoughtful girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8120184262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな軽率なことをするとは、やっぱり考えられないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't imagine her doing something so reckless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "で、でも……見ちゃったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… we saw it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1889574687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが男の人とホテルに入って行くところを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We saw Yu-chan going into a hotel with a man.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4783437401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……あの、すみれ？　昨日も言ったけどパパって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ Sumire? Like I said yesterday‚ she called him \"Papa\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3889574687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "呼んでたしやっぱり本当のお父さんなんじゃ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe he really is her real father…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3721952774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは絶対ないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's definitely not true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.122290802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんだって二人の話を聞いてたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ you heard their conversation‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2556241353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……確か「パパ、上手だから」とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… she said something like \"Papa‚ you're so good\" and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6889574687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かった、それ以上言わなくていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it‚ you don't need to say any more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.222290802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……見間違いじゃ、ないんだな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It wasn't a mistake‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達が、優を見間違えるなんてありえません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way we could mistake Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9967809041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "声も聞きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We even heard her voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3301142375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "し、しかし……優のお母さんは大女優で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… Yu's mother is a famous actress and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9634475708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんは大企業の経営者だったはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "her father is a big company executive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "パパ活なんてする理由がない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She has no reason to be needed a sugar daddy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6685044606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "百歩譲って、年上の恋人という線は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if we consider the possibility of an older boyfriend…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "恋人のこと、「パパ」って呼ぶと思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you think she'd call a boyfriend \"Papa\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5513162295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……呼ばないよな、普通",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ normally she wouldn't.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7513162295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ、本当のお父さんじゃない……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ if he's not her real father…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7794796466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、恋人でもないんだとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and not her boyfriend either‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5128129799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……すみれの言う通りなのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Maybe Sumire is right.",
        "id": ""
