      "text": "あるいは厄介な事件に巻き込まれてる可能性も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or she might be involved in some troubling situation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "優があの男の人に騙されてるってことですか！？",
